nodes.text: The Durosian fighter was a type of starfighter active during the First Order/Resistance War. One Durosian fighter was part of the citizens' fleet led by General Lando Calrissian during the Battle of Exegol between the Resistance and the Sith Eternal.
Durosian fighters first appeared in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker, the third and final installment of the Star Wars sequel trilogy.
